Attribution and Notice
======================

This repository is a derivative work based on:

- Upstream project: https://github.com/f/textream
- Upstream maintainer: Fatih Kadir Akin (https://fka.dev)
- Original idea credit (as stated by upstream): Semih Kislar (https://x.com/semihdev)

What this repository adds:

- Chinese localization and UX copy adaptation
- Local speech model integration workflow (SenseVoice)
- Matching stability improvements for repeated Chinese text

